		        <h2 class="header">ABOUT US</h2>
		        <p class="grey-text text-darken-3 lighten-3">Matara Food Solutions was created to provide easily accessible and delivered ingredients and other requirements to the home cooks, bakers and small restaurant owners in Sri Lanka.Starting with Matara and the suburbs, CFS stocks a range of high-quality ingredients for quick supply. Although some ingredients are from around the world, CFS aims to support Sri Lankan made products by sourcing and curating the best in the country. Our aim is to give small scale caterers, home bakers and other establishments the same sourcing opportunities as large enterprises to support and promote up and coming small businesses.</p>
